                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#3r">f. 3r</locus>
                           <desc>: Beginning of the hymn Ṭäbibä ṭäbiban "The Wisest among the Wisest Ones".</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="3r">3r</locus>: ኦእግዚኦ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ጠቢበ፡ ጠቢባን፡ ከሃሊ፡ ለአለም፡ እምጥንት፡ እንተ፡ ኢተበሊ…  </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The beginning of Text I (initially missing), has been written, in a secondary hand, in red and black, in the margins of <locus target="3r">3r</locus> (the same portion of text is written on the added <locus target="2v">2v</locus>
                           <note>).
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#30rb">f. 30rb</locus>
                           <desc>: Excerpt from a mälkǝʾa-hymn for John the Baptist. </desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez"> <locus target="30rb">30rb</locus>: ሰላም፡ ለበድነ፡ ስጋከ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ዜናዊ። ምጻተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ሰርቃዊ። እምከና[...]፡ ብዕሲት፡ ካልዕት፡ ወእመሰገርት፡ ነአዊ። ኦካሀን፡ ትምምክሀተ፡ ቤቱ፡ ለሌዊ፡ ለምንት፡ ሞትከ፡ እምይሙት፡ ዘማዊ። </quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note>
                           Crudely written in green ink.
                        </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ጠቢበ፡ ጠቢባን is crudely written on the front cover with yellow paint and on <locus target="1r">1r</locus>. (here written twice in blue and black pen).&#xD;
- The first five lines of <locus target="3ra">3ra</locus> are framed in a square, apparently indicating that it is repeated in <locus target="2vb">2vb</locus>. &#xD;
- First nine lines of Text III-2 are written on <locus target="30ra">30ra</locus>.&#xD;
- Hardly readable note in pencil in which a date is partly visible: <locus target="32v">32v</locus>: &#xD;
- Writing excercises on <locus target="32v">32v</locus>.&#xD;
- Pen trials: fols.1v, 4rb.</item>
                     </list>
